transcripts: Hey guys I'm Ahren back designer here at jansport and today I'm going to walk you through some awesome new products. Today we're going to look at the Cortlandt it's part of our classic collection it's a 25 later pack it features 600 denier polyester as well as a full synthetic leather bottom and trim details on the back of this pack you've got a nice big wedding hall loop as well as really nicely padded straight straps with an air mesh underneath and a full padded back panel the main compartment opens nice and wide really nice and big to reveal your 15 inch padded laptop sleeve and a 10-inch padded and treecko line tablet sleeve for that is a nice big flat pocket this is a great dump zone for both your items also has an organizer panel in front of that is a small zippered pocket great for a charger or any other small items you want easy access to on the go so there you have it your cortlandt as always guaranteed for life.
